title: SEIR-HCD Model
description: SEIR-HCD ModelThis is a working example of a SIER model with added compartments for HCD. The letters stand for:  Susceptible Exposed Infected Recovered Hospitalized Critical Death  I have adapted the equations from these great web apps:  http://gabgoh.github.io/COVID/index.html https://neherlab.org/covid19  NOTE: If you are looking for the SIER model, check commit 20 or earlier.
